  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图来展示Alice和John之间的简单问候场景。Alice先主动打招呼，John再回应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "问候场景"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，我理解为两个参与者Alice和John。Alice发起消息，John回复。请问他们是普通对象还是外部参与者？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "参与者类型"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "用actor类型吧，表示他们是外部角色。Alice发送的消息内容是\"Hello John, how are you?\"，John回复\"Great!\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "actor",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "Great!"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，Alice作为actor，发送问候消息给John，John作为actor回复。我注意到这两步都是异步消息，用虚线箭头表示，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "异步消息",
        "虚线箭头"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Alice到John的那条应该是同步调用，用实线叉号表示，表示Alice在等待回应。John回复Alice才是异步的虚线叉号。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "同步调用",
        "实线叉号",
        "异步回复",
        "虚线叉号"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，修正为：Alice-xJohn是同步调用（实线叉号），John--xAlice是异步回复（虚线叉号）。我这就绘制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice-xJohn",
        "John--xAlice",
        "同步调用",
        "异步回复"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已生成序列图：actor Alice和actor John，Alice发送同步消息\"Hello John, how are you?\"给John，John异步回复\"Great!\"给Alice。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Alice",
        "John",
        "Hello John, how are you?",
        "Great!",
        "actor"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美，就是这个效果。同步调用体现Alice主动发起并等待，异步回复体现John的独立响应。",
